                </p>
                <h3 style="margin-top: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--primary-color);">
                    Key Features
                </h3>
                <ul style="list-style-position: inside; color: var(--text-secondary);">
                    <li>Easy student registration with comprehensive data collection</li>
                    <li>View and manage all registered students in one place</li>
                    <li>Real-time statistics and analytics dashboard</li>
                    <li>Search and filter functionality for quick access</li>
                    <li>Responsive design that works on all devices</li>
                    <li>Clean and modern user interface</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
